<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN365">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>mayaṅkiruṅ karuviya vicumpumuka ṉāka</l>
<l>viyaṅkiya virucuṭar kaṇṇeṉap peyariya</l>
<l>vaḷiyiṭai vaḻaṅkā vaḻakkaru nīttam</l>
<l>vayirak kuṟaṭṭiṉ vayaṅkumaṇi yārattup</l>
<l>poṉṉan tikiri muṉcamat turuṭṭip</l>
<l>porunark kāṇāc cerumiku muṉpiṉ</l>
<l>muṉṉōr cellavuñ cellā tiṉṉum</l>
<l>vilainalap peṇṭiriṉ palarmīk kūṟa</l>
<l>vuḷḷēṉ vāḻiyar yāṉeṉap paṉmā</l>
<l>ṇilamaka ḷaḻuta kāñciyu</l>
<l>muṇṭeṉa vuraipparā luṇarntici ṉōrē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>While, </l>
<l>with the sky as a face that has masses of obscure dark [clouds], (1)</l>
<l>while the two stirring luminaries are named as eyes, (2)</l>
<l>in the flood difficult to navigate when the wind does not roam in between, (3)</l>
<l>with a string of glowing gems with a diamond frontlet (4)</l>
<l>rolling to the front battle on golden wheels, (5)</l>
<l>which much strength in fight which is not seen by fighters, (6)</l>
<l>not going even now, although those before did go, (7)</l>
<l>while many praise, like women whose beauty has a price, (8)</l>
<l>saying many times “I exist – let them live”, (9)</l>
<l>the lady earth cries, also transience exists, (10)</l>
<l>so say those indeed who have understood [the world]. (11)</l>
</lg>
    </div>
